    "RS485: TX=GPIO16, RX=GPIO17.",
    "AI: A1/A2 0-5V (GPIO5/7), A3/A4 4-20mA (GPIO6/4).",
    "SSD1306 128x64 OLED display on I2C 0x3C.",
    "Removable relay terminals — easier installation.",
    "Free GPIOs (with pull-up): 48, 47, 21, 15. Free GPIOs (no pull-up): 13, 14."
